    10→// Module:        module_77.go
    11→// Description:   Real-time sentiment routing component.  Consumes canonical
    12→//                SocialEvents, dynamically selects an inference strategy
    13→//                (high-accuracy vs low-latency) via the Strategy pattern,
    14→//                emits Prediction artifacts to downstream observers, and
    15→//                reports basic metrics.  Intended to sit behind the event
    16→//                bus consumer group and in front of the feature store.
    17→//
    18→// NOTE: This file is self-contained for illustrative purposes.  In a real
    19→//       code-base the ModelClient, registry, and protobufs would live in
    20→//       dedicated packages and be code-generated from .proto definitions.
